name: Memento Mauri #8
description: Urban Legends shared from the mouths of average citizens tell of a Soul fractured by the perils of Modern Living. "Mr. Smiley" they call him, a Dual Dirk wielding maniac sporting Hit 80's Band Goosran Goosran Apparel, Noise Cancelling Headphones (probably blasting Goosran), and the Infamous Cracked Smiley Mask.
